    (26,1,"Bedroll","Adventuring Gear",0.10,5.00,"<p>You never know where you're going to sleep, and a bedroll helps you get better sleep in a hayloft or on the cold ground. A bedroll consists of bedding and a blanket thin enough to be rolled up and tied. In an emergency, it can double as a stretcher.</p>"),
