    (67,1,"Piton","Adventuring Gear",0.10,0.50,"<p>When a wall doesn't offer handholds and footholds, you can make your own. A piton is a steel spike with an eye through which you can loop a rope. (See the Climb skill)</p>"),
    (68,1,"Pole, 10-foot","Adventuring Gear",0.20,8.00,"<p>When you suspect a trap, you can put the end of your 10-foot pole through that hole in the wall instead of reaching with your hand.</p>"),
